caption:
Eating disorders are complex, serious, and often misunderstood. Swipe through to learn key facts – like how eating disorders often develop alongside mental health conditions like anxiety and depression, OCD and ADHD, and how anyone can develop an eating disorder regardless of gender, age, race, and body size.

If you or someone you love is experiencing an eating disorder, the time to seek help is now. You do not have to struggle in silence. 🤐 #EatingDisordersAwarenessMonth
